Sentence.Text: I buy some seeds at the store.
The first day, I sow the seeds in the soil.
The next day, the seeds germinate and the sprouts grow.
The day after, the green plants grow.
The day after that, a huge storm comes.
The plants are killed by flooding.
I put the leftover seeds on my belly.
I cover my belly to keep the seeds warm.
I am a tree planting robot!
